## User Story

```md
As a USER I want to enter my recipes
So that they will list in order of quickest cooktimes
And display last recipe entered prominently
```

## Acceptance Criteria

GIVEN I'd need a personal recipe blog
WHEN I load the app
THEN I am presented with a page containing 'add recipe' and stored recipes
WHEN I click 'add recipe' I am given a form to enter in recipe title, information, and cooktime
THEN when I click submit it will add information to locally stored recipes and display
WHEN I click delete recipe 
THEN The displayed recipe will be deleted along with the locally stored recipe
WHEN I change the page size or view on a smaller device
THEN I am presented with an responsive layout that changes to my viewport


